//000000000000a:2:{i:0;a:4:{s:2:"id";s:2:"30";s:5:"title";s:12:"算法运算";s:7:"content";s:4401:"<p>1. 问题描述: 八进制转十进制</p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">八进制和十进制的区别,八进制逢8进1,十进制逢10进1,所以八进制每次进1比十进制小2;
070&nbsp;八进制表示,转换成十进制是56,&nbsp;070表示的是八进制进位了7次,那么转换成十进制就是:&nbsp;7*10-7*2=56;&nbsp;答案正确;
随便猜想一个数字,用来验证这个方案的可行性.&nbsp;
073(八进制),7*8+3=59;
0361(八进制)&nbsp;(3*8+6)*8+1=241&nbsp;(十进制);(用计算器核对,正确)
最后发现其实就是:&nbsp;3*8^2+6*8^1+1*8^0=241&nbsp;&nbsp;(类似十进制:3*10^2+6*10^1+1*10^0=361)
代码实现:&nbsp;八进制数num,转换十进制;
function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum=0&nbsp;){
	$len&nbsp;=&nbsp;strlen($num);
	$sum&nbsp;+=&nbsp;intval($num/pow(10,$len-1)&nbsp;)*pow(8,$len-1);
	if(&nbsp;$len==1&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;}
	$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;$num%pow(10,$len-1);
	return&nbsp;convert($num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum);
}
echo&nbsp;convert(361);</pre><p>2. 问题描述: 十进制转八进制<br/></p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">361(十进制)&nbsp;转换成八进制是多少呢?&nbsp;3*10^2+6*10^1+1*10^0&nbsp;(十进制)
代码实现:&nbsp;十进制转换八进制
function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,$sum=&#39;&#39;&nbsp;){
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$len&nbsp;=&nbsp;strlen($num);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;.=&nbsp;intval($num/pow(8,$len-1));
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(&nbsp;$len&nbsp;==&nbsp;1&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;$num%pow(8,$len-1);&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;);
}
echo&nbsp;convert(361);
有一点不同的是,这里采取的是字符串String拼接方法.那么修改下:
function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,$sum=0&nbsp;){
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$len&nbsp;=&nbsp;strlen($num);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;+=&nbsp;intval($num/pow(8,$len-1))*pow(10,$len-1);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(&nbsp;$len&nbsp;==&nbsp;1&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;$num%pow(8,$len-1);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;);
}
echo&nbsp;convert(361);
可以发现,八进制转换成十进制和十进制转换成八进制的代码是近乎一样的.因此两个代码可以公用:
function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;&nbsp;,&nbsp;$source&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,$sum=0&nbsp;){
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$len&nbsp;=&nbsp;strlen($num);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;+=&nbsp;intval($num/pow($aim,$len-1))*pow($source,$len-1);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(&nbsp;$len&nbsp;==&nbsp;1&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;$num%pow($aim,$len-1);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$source&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,$sum&nbsp;);
}
echo&nbsp;convert(361,8,10);
以上只能对十进制和八进制有效,原因是因为8和10相近,不会出现intval($num/pow($aim,$len-1))&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;$aim
如果出现这种情况,那么肯定就出错了.</pre><p>3. 问题描述: 十进制转二进制</p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,$sum=&#39;&#39;&nbsp;){
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;.=&nbsp;$num%$aim;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;intval($num/$aim);
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;==&nbsp;0&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;&nbsp;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;);
}
echo&nbsp;strrev(convert(371,2));
当然,这里也能处理十进制转换成其他的进制,然而输入的数值都是十进制表示的.
优化之后:
function&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,$sum=&#39;&#39;&nbsp;){
	$temp&nbsp;=&nbsp;log($aim&nbsp;,&nbsp;2);
	$sum&nbsp;.=&nbsp;$num%$aim;
	$num&nbsp;=&nbsp;$num&gt;&gt;$temp;
	if(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;==&nbsp;0&nbsp;){&nbsp;return&nbsp;$sum;&nbsp;}
	return&nbsp;convert(&nbsp;$num&nbsp;,&nbsp;$aim&nbsp;,&nbsp;$sum&nbsp;);
}
echo&nbsp;strrev(convert(10,2));
转换的进制只能是2的倍数.</pre><p>4. 问题描述: 随意输入一个进制的数值,然后可以随意转换成一个进制数值.</p><p>第一种办法: 将所有的输入数值转换成十进制,在转换成输出进制,可行,效率不高;</p><p><br/></p>";s:7:"created";s:10:"1464763210";}i:1;a:4:{s:2:"id";s:2:"29";s:5:"title";s:9:"php相关";s:7:"content";s:20392:"<p style="text-align: justify; "><span style="color:#454545;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">职位要求</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">岗位职责：</span><br style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1. 负责公司线上产品开发、维护、及BUG修复；</span><br style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2. 负责网站平台相关业务模块的分析、设计；</span><br style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3. 参于各项目中的编码工作；</span><br style="color: